Incident Quotes:
I entrust to God my sisters, the light of my heart (Doha Bassam Qariqa and Saja Bassam Qariqa), and those who have passed away from my family: my aunt and second mother, Inam Qariqa (Um Yahya), and her daughter, Maryam Qariqa;

 my uncle, Awad Qariqa (Abu Hazem);

 my beloved cousin, the artist Muhammad Sami Qariqa (Abu Sami); and the child, Muhammad Ghassan Qariqa, 

after their martyrdom in the massacre at Al-Ahli Baptist Hospital. — https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1BinWbGUSG/

