Telegram: Martyr Commander/ Awad Suleiman Qariqa

(Commander in the Military Judiciary Unit - Gaza Brigade)
Facebook: I entrust to God my sisters, the light of my heart (Doha Bassam Qariqa and Saja Bassam Qariqa), and those who have passed away from my family: my aunt and second mother, Inam Qariqa (Um Yahya), and her daughter, Maryam Qariqa;

 my uncle, Awad Qariqa (Abu Hazem);

 my beloved cousin, the artist Muhammad Sami Qariqa (Abu Sami); and the child, Muhammad Ghassan Qariqa, 

after their martyrdom in the massacre at Al-Ahli Baptist Hospital.

Facebook: With profound sorrow and grief, and in submission to God's will and decree, we received the news of the martyrdom of a group of our dear comrades: the martyr, 
the mujahid Hamada Salman; 
the martyr, the mujahid Youssef Hajouj; 
and the martyr, the mujahid Ibrahim Halawa. 
Congratulations on your martyrdom. 
Indeed, you were truly noble men. May God accept you among the highest ranks of Paradise. It is fitting that one who lived courageously should die a martyr.

